metadata.name: Full Pink Moon #1
metadata.description:
On this saturday night, the full pink moon is just in front of me.
This is my first try to shot it, I hope, like me, you appreciate how this moment is quiet; just you and the moon !

Artist: ChrisKoool

Collection: Full Pink Moon

Edition: 1/1
